# Module 2: Prompt Engineering for Developers – Participant Guide

## 📝 Overview
Learn to craft effective prompts for coding, debugging, and documentation.

## 🎯 Learning Objectives
- Design high-quality prompts for consistent outputs
- Build a library of reusable prompt templates

## 🚀 Activities
1. Revise a bad prompt into a good one
2. Create a prompt for setting up a React+Node.js project
3. Peer test prompts with partners

## 🔗 References
- [OpenAI Prompt Optimization](https://platform.openai.com/docs/guides/optimizing-llm-accuracy)
- [Prompt Caching](https://platform.openai.com/docs/guides/prompt-caching)
